<h1>About CityExplorer</h1>

<div class="card mb-4">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>Project Overview</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p>CityExplorer helps users discover restaurants and landmarks in various cities, along with user reviews.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>Data Sources</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <ul class="list-group">
      <li class="list-group-item">
        <strong>Faker Gem:</strong> Generated <%= Restaurant.count %> restaurants, <%= Landmark.count %> landmarks, and <%= Review.count %> reviews
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        <strong>CSV Import (Coming Soon):</strong> Will add real restaurant data from public datasets
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        <strong>OpenStreetMap API (Coming Soon):</strong> Will add geocoding for addresses
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>Database Schema</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <pre>
Restaurants
- id (integer)
- name (string)
- cuisine (string)
- address (string)
- price_range (string)
- rating (float)
- lat (float)
- lng (float)

Landmarks
- id (integer)
- name (string)
- category (string)
- address (string)
- description (text)
- lat (float)
- lng (float)

Reviews (polymorphic)
- id (integer)
- reviewable_id (integer)
- reviewable_type (string)
- rating (integer)
- comment (text)
- user_name (string)
    </pre>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>Statistics</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <ul class="list-group">
      <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        Total Restaurants
        <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill"><%= Restaurant.count %></span>
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        Total Landmarks
        <span class="badge bg-success rounded-pill"><%= Landmark.count %></span>
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        Total Reviews
        <span class="badge bg-warning rounded-pill"><%= Review.count %></span>
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        Total Records
        <span class="badge bg-info rounded-pill"><%= Restaurant.count + Landmark.count + Review.count %></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
<p class='text-muted text-center mt-3'>Last updated: <%= Time.current.strftime('%B %Y') %></p>
